<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stone-n">stone <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stəʊn/    美 /stoʊn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>石头；石料</strong></h4>
<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>石块；石子</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3">3.<strong>宝石</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="a-stepping-stone">a stepping stone</h3>
<p>1.<strong>垫脚石；藉以达到目标的手段或阶段</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="a-stones-throw">a stone’s throw</h3>
<p>1.<strong>很近的距离；不远处：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At that time my family lived a stone’s throw from his.
那时我家离他家很近。</p><footer>2012 福建改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>stony /'stəʊni/ adj   </p></div>